{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"TLT\n      \n        @keyframes morph1{0%{d:path('M0,60 Q50,20 100,50 Q150,80 200,40 Q250,10 300,50 Q350,70 400,30 L400,100 L0,100 Z')}100%{d:path('M0,40 Q50,60 100,30 Q150,50 200,70 Q250,30 300,60 Q350,40 400,50 L400,100 L0,100 Z')}}\n        @keyframes morph2{0%{d:path('M0,70 Q60,30 120,60 Q180,90 240,40 Q300,20 360,55 Q380,65 400,45 L400,100 L0,100 Z')}100%{d:path('M0,50 Q60,70 120,40 Q180,60 240,80 Q300,40 360,65 Q380,45 400,55 L400,100 L0,100 Z')}}\n        @keyframes globe{0%{transform:translateX(-50%) rotate(0deg)}100%{transform:translateX(-50%) rotate(360deg)}}\n      \n    \n    \n      C — Living Terrain\n      Vibe: Organic, immersive, world-building. Think Webflow meets award-winning Awwwards sites.\n      A 3D landscape that morphs and evolves as you scroll. Mountains rise, oceans form, cities emerge. The terrain reflects the agency's journey with each section. Interactive globe for the portfolio. Volumetric fog and atmospheric lighting create depth.\n      Tech: React Three Fiber + custom terrain shaders. Displacement maps, fog, environment maps.","choice":"c","id":null,"timestamp":1775368498005}
